" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship.html\">Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/proof-citizenship.html\">Get proof of Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/proof-citizenship/search-records.html\">Search of citizenship records</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nSearch of citizenship records: After you apply</h1>\n<div><div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"gc-stp-stp mrgn-tp-md mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<ul class=\"toc lst-spcd col-md-12\">\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/proof-citizenship/search-records.html\">1. About the process</a></li>\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/proof-citizenship/search-records/how-to-apply.html\">2. How to apply</a></li>\n<li class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-6\"><a class=\"list-group-item active\">3. After you apply</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">Processing your application</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"process-covid-cit-eng\"></span>\n<!--<div class=\"well\">\n  <p><a href=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/coronavirus-covid19/citizenship.html#s2\"><img class=\"img-responsive pull-left mrgn-rght-md\" src=\"/content/dam/ircc/images/services/coronavirus-covid19/covid-icon-new.png\" alt=\"\">Find out how COVID-19 affects the processing of your citizenship application</a>.</p>\n</div>-->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-5 pull-right col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"mwspanel section\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-primary\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h3 class=\"panel-title\">Processing time</h3>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p class=\"h1 mrgn-tp-sm\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-time\"></span> <span data-json-replace=\"#[ptime]/citizenship/cit_search\">We couldn't load the data. Try again.</span> <sup class=\"small\"><a aria-controls=\"processing-times\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#processing-times\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign\"></span><span class=\"sr-only\">?</span></a></sup></p>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"processing-times\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title\">Processing times</h2>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Processing times will vary based on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>the type of application submitted</li>\n<li>if the application is complete</li>\n<li>how quickly we expect to process applications we’ve already received</li>\n<li>how easily we can verify your information</li>\n<li>how long you take to respond to any requests or concerns</li>\n<li>other factors</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Learn how processing times are <a href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=068&amp;top=3\">calculated</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<p>Processing time is the average for how long it takes from when an application is received to when we make a decision. </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/results-by-topic.asp?st=3.2\">Learn more about processing times</a></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n\t\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/ircc/documents/json/data-ptime-non-country-en.json\",\n\t\t\"name\": \"ptime\"\n\t}' id=\"jsonmanagernoncountry\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-auto\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<p>Answer a few questions to know</p>\n<ul>\n<li>what happens after you submit your application</li>\n<li>how to update and track your application during processing</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"wb-frmvld hidden\" id=\"pe-ff\">\n<form>\n<div class=\"wb-fieldflow\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\"noForm\": true, \"unhideelm\": \"#pe-ff\", \"hideelm\": \"#online, #can-us, #outside-email, #outside-no-email\", \"renderas\":\"radio\", \n\t\"base\":{\"live\":true},\n\t\"default\":{\"action\":\"addClass\",\"source\":\"#online, #can-us, #outside-email, #outside-no-email\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}}'>\n<p>How did you apply?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\",\"source\":\"#online\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}'>Online</li>\n<li>On paper\n          <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\"renderas\":\"radio\"}'>\n<p>Where did you apply from?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\",\"source\":\"#can-us\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}'>Canada</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\",\"source\":\"#can-us\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}'>United States</li>\n<li>Outside Canada and the United States\n                <div class=\"wb-fieldflow-sub\" data-wb-fieldflow='{\"renderas\":\"radio\"}'>\n<p>Did you provide an email address in your application form?</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\",\"source\":\"#outside-email\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}'>Yes</li>\n<li data-wb-fieldflow='{\"action\":\"removeClass\",\"source\":\"#outside-no-email\",\"class\":\"hidden\"}'>No</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div id=\"can-us\">\n<!--CANDADA-US -->\n<h2>After you applied on paper from Canada or the United States</h2>\n<p>If you have a tracking number with a postal or courier service, you can check when your application gets delivered to us.</p>\n<p>Once we get your application for a search of citizenship records, we’ll check if it’s complete. If it is, we’ll start processing it. We won’t automatically send you a confirmation.</p>\n<div class=\"well well-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\">If your application is incomplete</h3>\n<p>If something is missing, we’ll return your application and ask for the missing information.</p></div>\n<h3>Track and update your application</h3>\n<p>During processing, track and update your application by</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\" target=\"blank\">checking the status of your application</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li>telling us if you <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/change-address.html\" target=\"blank\">change your address</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form2.html\" target=\"blank\">contacting us via the web form</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> to update other information in your application</li>\n</ul>\n<details>\n<summary><h4>If you need urgent processing</h4></summary>\n<p>We can process applications faster than our normal <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/times/canada/certif-processing.asp\">processing times</a> in <strong>special cases</strong>, such as</p>\n<ul>\n<li>confirming to a foreign government that you’re <strong>not</strong> a citizen\n            <ul>\n<li>For example, to get a passport from that country.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>showing you are (or are not) a citizen to get a certain job</li>\n<li>administering the estate of a deceased person or executing a will</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To ask for urgent processing of your <strong>submitted</strong> application</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fill out our <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form2.html\" target=\"blank\">web form</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span>. </li>\n<li>include<ul>\n<li>your full name, date of birth, email address and telephone numbers</li>\n<li>a letter explaining why you need urgent processing</li>\n<li><a aria-controls=\"_Examples_of_supporting_1\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#_Examples_of_supporting_1\" role=\"button\">any documents</a> that support your request for urgent processing\n        <ul>\n<li>Make sure your document is in the <a aria-controls=\"_File_format_requirements_1_1\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#_File_format_requirements_1_1\" role=\"button\">correct format</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n<p>We’ll review your request to see if it qualifies. <strong>Even if you qualify, we can’t guarantee that you’ll get your search of citizenship record on time.</strong></p></div>\n</details>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"_File_format_requirements_1_1\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h5 class=\"modal-title\">File format requirements</h5>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>When you upload files, they must be</p>\n<ul>\n<li>in PDF, JPEG, TIFF, DOC, or DOCX format</li>\n<li>2 MB or smaller</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you include multiple files, the total size must be 3.5 MB or smaller.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1213&amp;top=23\" target=\"blank\">How to reduce file size</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"_Examples_of_supporting_1\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h5 class=\"modal-title\">Examples of supporting documents</h5>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Some examples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A letter from a foreign government stating that they need the information.</li>\n<li>Documents that show you’re administering an estate or the executor of a will.</li>\n<li>A letter from an employer.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>Get your search result</h3>\n<p>We’ll email you a printable PDF letter with the search result. </p>\n<p>If you asked for a paper copy, we’ll mail it to your mailing address in Canada or the United States.</p>\n<ul><li>It’s <strong>valid for 1 year</strong>. \n        <ul>\n<li>If the person whose record you searched for is deceased, the letter doesn’t expire.</li>\n</ul>\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-ok\"></span> Record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>when the person became a Canadian citizen <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>if they have a Canadian citizenship application in progress</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove\"></span>No record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there’s no record <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>we can’t find a record with the information you gave us</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--ONLINE-->\n<div id=\"online\">\n<h2>After you apply online</h2>\n<p>After you submit your online application, you’ll see a confirmation page. This page</p>\n<ul>\n<li>confirms you successfully submitted your application</li>\n<li>has a confirmation number\n                <ul>\n<li>keep it for your records</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You’ll also automatically get</p>\n<ul>\n<li>an acknowledgement of receipt (AOR) email, and</li>\n<li>an <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1521&amp;top=4\" target=\"_blank\">application number</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"well well-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\">If your application is incomplete</h3>\n<p>If something is missing, we’ll</p>\n<ul>\n<li>send a message in your account to ask for the missing information</li>\n<li>cancel your application if you don’t respond by the deadline in the message</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3>Track and update your application</h3>\n<p>During processing, track and update your application by</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\" target=\"blank\">checking the status of your application</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li>telling us if you <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/change-address.html\" target=\"blank\">change your address</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form2.html\" target=\"blank\">contacting us via the web form</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> to update other information in your application</li>\n</ul>\n<details>\n<summary><h4>If you need urgent processing</h4></summary>\n<p>We can process applications faster than our normal <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/times/canada/certif-processing.asp\">processing times</a> in <strong>special cases</strong>, such as</p>\n<ul>\n<li>confirming to a foreign government that you’re <strong>not</strong> a citizen \n                <ul>\n<li>For example, to get a passport from that country.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>showing you are (or are not) a citizen to get a certain job</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you need to ask for urgent processing of an online application you’ve already submitted</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fill out our <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc/web-form2.html\" target=\"blank\">web form</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> </li>\n<li>include\n                <ul>\n<li>your full name, date of birth, email address and telephone numbers</li>\n<li>a letter explaining why you need urgent processing</li>\n<li><a aria-controls=\"_Examples_of_supporting\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#_Examples_of_supporting\" role=\"button\">any documents</a> that support your request for urgent processing\n                    <ul>\n<li>Make sure your documents are in the <a aria-controls=\"_File_format_requirements_1\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#_File_format_requirements_1\" role=\"button\">correct format</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n<p>We’ll review your request to see if it qualifies. <strong>Even if you qualify, we can’t guarantee that you’ll get your search of citizenship record on time.</strong></p></div>\n</details>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"_Examples_of_supporting\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h5 class=\"modal-title\">Examples of supporting documents</h5>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Some examples:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A letter from a foreign government stating that they need the information.</li>\n<li>Documents that show you’re administering an estate or the executor of a will.</li>\n<li>A letter from an employer.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"_File_format_requirements_1\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h5 class=\"modal-title\">File format requirements</h5>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>When you upload files, they must be</p>\n<ul>\n<li>in PDF, JPEG, TIFF, DOC, or DOCX format</li>\n<li>2 MB or smaller</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you include multiple files, the total size must be 3.5 MB or smaller.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1213&amp;top=23\" target=\"blank\">How to reduce file size</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>Get your search result</h3>\n<p>We’ll send a letter with the search result to <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/account.html\" target=\"blank\">your online account</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It will be a PDF you can download and print.</li>\n<li>It’s <strong>valid for 1 year</strong>. \n            <ul>\n<li>If the person whose record you searched for is deceased, the letter doesn’t expire.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-ok\"></span> Record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>when the person became a Canadian citizen <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>if they have a Canadian citizenship application in progress</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove\"></span>No record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there’s no record <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>we can’t find a record with the information you gave us</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outside-email\">\n<!--<h2>Outside email result</h2>-->\n<h2>If you applied from outside Canada and the United States and provided an email</h2>\n<p>Once we receive your application for a search of citizenship records, we’ll check if it’s <strong>complete</strong>. If it is, we’ll start processing it. We won’t automatically send you a confirmation.</p>\n<div class=\"well well-sm\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\">If your application is incomplete</h3>\n<p>We’ll return your application and ask for the missing information.</p>\n</div>\n<h3>Track and update your application</h3>\n<p>During processing, track and update your application by:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\" target=\"_blank\">checking the status of your application</a><span class=\"wb-inv\"> (opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li>telling us if you <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/change-address.html\" target=\"_blank\">change your address</a><span class=\"wb-inv\"> (opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\" target=\"_blank\">contacting the embassy, high commission or consulate</a><span class=\"wb-inv\"> (opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> where you submitted your application (to update other information)</li>\n</ul>\n<details>\n<summary>\n<h4>If you need urgent processing</h4>\n</summary>\n<p>We can process applications faster than our normal <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/times/canada/certif-processing.asp\">processing times</a> in <strong>special cases</strong>, such as</p>\n<ul>\n<li>confirming to a foreign government that you’re <strong>not</strong> a citizen (for example, to get a passport from that country)</li>\n<li>administering the estate of a deceased person or executing a will</li>\n<li>showing you are (or are not) a citizen to get a certain job</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To ask for urgent processing of your <strong>submitted</strong> application, <a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\" target=\"_blank\">contact the Canadian embassy, consulate or high commission</a><span class=\"wb-inv\"> (opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> where you submitted your application.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning mrgn-tp-md\">\n<p>We’ll review your request to see if it qualifies. <strong>Even if you qualify, we can’t guarantee that you’ll get your search of citizenship record on time.</strong></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n<h3>Get your search result</h3>\n<p>We’ll email you a printable PDF.</p>\n<p>If you asked for a paper copy, we’ll mail your letter to the embassy, high commission or consulate <strong>where you submitted</strong> your application.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It’s <strong>valid for 1 year</strong>. \n            <ul>\n<li>If the person whose record you searched for is deceased, the letter doesn’t expire.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-ok\"></span> Record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>when the person became a Canadian citizen <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>if they have a Canadian citizenship application in progress</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove\"></span>No record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there’s no record <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>we can’t find a record with the information you gave us</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outside-no-email\">\n<!-- <h2>Outside no email result</h2>-->\n<h2>If you applied from outside Canada and the United States but didn’t provide an email</h2>\n<p>Once we receive your application for a search of citizenship records, we’ll check if it’s <strong>complete</strong>. If it is, we’ll start processing it. We won’t automatically send you a confirmation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\" target=\"_blank\">Contact the Canadian embassy, high commission or consulate</a> <span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> where you submitted your application to confirm that we received it.</p>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">If your application is incomplete</h3>\n<p>We’ll return your application and ask for the missing information.</p>\n</div>\n<h3>Track and update your application</h3>\n<p>During processing, track and update your application by</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\" target=\"_blank\">checking the status of your application</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li>telling us if you <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/change-address.html\" target=\"_blank\">change your address</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\" target=\"_blank\">contacting the embassy, high commission or consulate</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> where you submitted your application (to update other information)</li>\n</ul>\n<details>\n<summary>\n<h4>If you need urgent processing</h4>\n</summary>\n<p>We can process applications faster than our normal <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/times/canada/certif-processing.asp\">processing times</a> in <strong>special cases</strong>.</p>\n<p>You can ask for urgent processing if you need to </p>\n<ul>\n<li>confirm to a foreign government that you’re <strong>not</strong> a citizen (for example, to get a passport from that country)</li>\n<li>administer the estate of a deceased person or execute a will</li>\n<li>show you are (or are not) a citizen to get a certain job</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To ask for urgent processing of your <strong>submitted application</strong>, <a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/assistance/embassies-consulates\" target=\"_blank\">contact the Canadian embassy, consulate or high commission</a><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span> where you submitted your application.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning mrgn-tp-md\">\n<p>We’ll review your request to see if it qualifies. <strong>Even if you qualify, we can’t guarantee that you’ll get your search of citizenship record on time.</strong></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n<h3>Get your search result</h3>\n<p>We’ll mail your letter to the embassy, high commission or consulate <strong>where you submitted</strong> your application.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It’s <strong>valid for 1 year</strong>. \n            <ul>\n<li>If the person whose record you searched for is deceased, the letter doesn’t expire.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-ok\"></span> Record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>when the person became a Canadian citizen <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>if they have a Canadian citizenship application in progress</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\n<section class=\"panel panel-default hght-inhrt\">\n<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n<h4 class=\"panel-title h5 mrgn-tp-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove\"></span>No record found</h4>\n</header>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>We’ll send you a letter to tell you if</p>\n<ul>\n<li>there’s no record <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>we can’t find a record with the information you gave us</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-07-09\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/results-by-topic.asp?top=5\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc.html\"> Contact us</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\">Check your application status</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gc-main-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Government of Canada</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/contact.html\">All contacts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/dept.html\">Departments and